channel.title: In urgent need of help!Server won't go online!
channel.description:
Here's what i have done right(or think i have done right): I have correctly port-forwarded.(I think...) I have created a server. I have turned the server on. I have no-ip set up and running. I have compiled after any changes to the server. I have opened the ports on my computer.
Here's my problem: I can't post my server on the Server Status page. No one besides me can log onto my server. I have no clue why...???
